Desmond Harrington https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Desmond_Harrington 0 Desmond Harrington (born October 19, 1976) is an American actor. He has appeared in The Hole (2001), Ghost Ship (2002), and Wrong Turn (2003), joined the cast of the Showtime series Dexter in its third season, as Det. Joseph "Joey" Quinn, and appeared in some episodes of Gossip Girl. Desmond_Harrington ( born October_19_,_1976 ) is an_American_actor .
